metadata.description: Punk5js are reimagined and enhanced as generative canvases, using p5js generative art. To ensure the p5js renders correctly, please view your Punk5js on OpenSea or on http://www.punk5js.com/. The Images are interactive! To interact with the renders use your keyboard/mouse: A - Save a screenshot of the Punk5js canvas; R - Faster Generation; T - Slower Generation; Mouse Click - Delete Some of the Render... Note that on OS you may need to click the image to start using interaction.
metadata.name: Punk5js #1
